As Slag slammed into him, Pacifix began to tip, but he tried his best to
rerain from crying out in pain. Before he could tip all the way to his
side, he quickly detached and transformed. Looking straight into Prowl's
eyes as he stood up, he sounded confused. "If this is your base, then
aren't you the ones that need our help?"
